address: Xã Tân Hưng, Huyện Sóc Sơn, Thành phố Hà Nội
thought:
**Determining the New Administrative Unit for "Xã Tân Hưng"**

Okay, so the user wants to know the new administrative unit for "Xã Tân Hưng, Huyện Sóc Sơn, Thành phố Hà Nội." Let's break this down. First, I need to check if "Thành phố Hà Nội" has been merged with any other province. Based on my understanding of administrative changes, I know that Resolution 60-NQ/TW states that "Thành phố Hà Nội" remains unchanged. Good, that simplifies things.

Now, I'm diving into the "Other resolutions" section, specifically `1656/NQ-UBTVQH15`, which details the restructuring of wards in Hà Nội.  I'm scanning for "Xã Tân Hưng" within the document. Lines 122, 123, 124, and 126 are my focus.  Eureka! Line 123 clearly states that "Xã Tân Hưng" (along with other wards) will be merged into a new ward called "xã Đa Phúc."

To be absolutely certain, I'll cross-reference this information with the "New wards" list for "Thành phố Hà Nội". I'm looking for "xã Đa Phúc" in that list. Yes!  The entry `{"ward_code":"00430","ward_name":"Xã Đa Phúc","province_name":"Thành phố Hà Nội"}` confirms everything. It matches perfectly!

Therefore, my conclusion, with a high degree of confidence, is that "Xã Tân Hưng" is now part of "xã Đa Phúc" in "Thành phố Hà Nội". This is what I'll report back.
